            <iframe 
                id="gameFrame" 
                class="game-frame" 
                src="https://www.nytimes.com/games/wordle/index.html"
                style="display: none;"
                frameborder="0"
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
            <div class="error-message" id="errorMessage" style="display: none;">
                <h3>🚫 Game temporarily unavailable</h3>
                <p>This might be due to network issues or server maintenance. Please try:</p>
                <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 30px; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Refresh the page to reload</li>
                    <li>Check your internet connection</li>
                    <li>Try another popular game</li>
                    <li>Wait a moment and try again</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="retry-btn" onclick="retryLoad()">🔄 Retry Loading</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="game-info" id="gameInfo">
            <h3>🎱 Slope - 3D Ball Rolling Speed Challenge</h3>
            <p>Slope is an incredibly thrilling 3D ball rolling game! Control the green ball as it speeds down endless slopes, dodging red obstacles and testing your reaction limits. The game gets faster and more challenging as you progress - one mistake and it's game over. Simple controls, extreme challenge, absolutely addictive!</p>
